<p>Heuristics</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>What would I think if I was another type of person? Different Identity?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Habits</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Environment as Main Determinant of Behavior (Social and Physical)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Assume that some options are eliminated</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>When we consider the best and worst states, what context do we think exists?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Which dogs didn’t bark (what did I expect to see that did not exist?)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Frog in boiling water (what slow changes are impacting the system?)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Tight / Aggressive approach to decisions (Focus tradeoff)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Pareto Principle (80/20 rule, Curate, Triage)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>No Brainer (Do the Obvious Thing)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Maslow’s Hammer (The tools you have determine the solutions you see)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Invert</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>History</p>

<ol>
